Version 0.1 (Alpha)
--------------------
Date: November 2010

    * It's currently implementing:
          o A simple website framework
                + PHP core
                + HTML / CSS / Javascript presentation
          o Multinlingual (french, english, spanish), language files
          o Two levels automatically build menu
          o Utils php functions
          o Customized error pages
          o Embedding simpletest test framework (http://www.simpletest.org/), not used for now.
          o Embedding draft documentation
          o XHTML validation: Valid XHTML 1.0 Strict

Version 0.2 (Beta)
-------------------
Date: April 2011

    * It will implement:
          o Error pages localized
          o Tests of utlis functions, with simpletest framework
          o Documentation completed
          o Include a simple web-based WYSIWYG editor, written in MooTools:
                + http://cheeaun.github.com/mooeditable/
                + On github: https://github.com/cheeaun/mooeditable

